      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly i dont even know why i bother coming to these cafes or working or anything. like i'm just sitting here in this city where nobody knows my name and if i just stopped showing up tomorrow.. i don't think it would even matter. it feels like i'm just taking up space that could be used for someone who actually exists.",
